OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome brightness in the north
OL,6,Ffirst thing, however extensive low
OL,7,Fcloud further south spreading north.
OL,8,FMostly dry but some patchy little rain
OL,9,For drizzle possible. A slightly milder
OL,10,Fday than on Saturday for most, with
OL,11,Fgenerally light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud tending to lower
OL,14,Fovernight with mist, patchy fog and
OL,15,Fhill fog becoming more widespread
OL,16,Fagain. Winds remaining generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
